{assign var="active" value="frequentquestion"}

<div class="row login">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-9">
            <div class="shopyheader">
                <h2>{l s='General questions' mod='shopylinkerp'}</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-10 shopyinfopanel">
                <h2>{l s='General questions' mod='shopylinkerp'}</h2>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question1" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="question1">
                        {l s='What is Shopylinker for PrestaShop?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse in" id="question1">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            {l s='Shopylinker is much more than a module for PrestaShop, Shopylinker is a complementary management system that provides a large number of advantages for the store:' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    {l s='Facilitates the management and optimization of the catalog with the aim of improving organic positioning and improving the user experience' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    {l s='Improves the security of the store by facilitating the creation of backups and their subsequent recovery if necessary.' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    {l s='Improve store control by recording user actions' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    {l s='Provides the most complete import / export system' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    {l s='It makes it easy to have the store in the latest version thanks to the continuous maintenance included with the subscription.' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    {l s='Includes more than 20 modules and multiple built-in additional functionalities' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                                </li>
                            </ul>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HAnsqIaC7MA"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Introduction to Shopylinker' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Video"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question2" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question2">
                        {l s='How is the catalog managed with Shopylinker?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question2">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s='Through an innovative visual and intuitive workspace, made up of 5 work environments, all of them combined with the massive actions container, the catalog is managed easily and quickly and in a perfectly informed manner.' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question3" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question3">
                        {l s='How can you increase sales with Shopylinker?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse " id="question3">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s='Shopylinker provides the necessary tools to optimize the natural content of the store, that is, the content of the catalog to improve SEO positioning and the user experience in the store, thereby increasing the number of visits to the store and the conversion rate to sales.' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question4" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question4">
                        {l s='What does the subscription to Shopylinker include?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse " id="question4">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s='There are 3 types of subscriptions to Shopylinker which in summary consist of:' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                {l s='Essential Plan: Provides the catalog management and optimization system, including Import / Export' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                {l s='Advanced Plan: Add to the Essential plan the set of modules necessary to fully exploit the advantages of the optimized catalog' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                {l s='Professional Plan: Add to the Advanced plan a complete logistics management system, points of sale in physical stores and order management' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/plans/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='Visit our plans page' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question5" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question5">
                        {l s='What is the price of Shopylinker?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse " id="question5">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <a class="linkinfo" href="https://shopylinker.com/en/plans/"
                               target="_blank">{l s='You can check Shopylinker prices at: https://shopylinker.com/en/plans/' mod='shopylinkerp'}<i
                                        class="icon_Abrir_pagina"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question6" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question6">
                        {l s='What additional expense does Shopylinker entail for my store?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse " id="question6">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s='If you consider the set of modules included and compare them with the alternative of purchasing the modules separately, you will quickly realize that Shopylinker generates a significant reduction in expenses.' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                {l s='Add to this reduction the time savings needed to manage the catalog, which can only be achieved using the Shopylinker workspace, and you will see your expenses drop even more.' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                {l s='And if we also consider the increase in sales generated by the guided optimization of the catalog to increase sales, an exclusive Shopylinker tool, you will come to the conclusion that using Shopylinker not only does not imply an additional expense, but also reduces expenses and increases income.' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question7" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question7">
                        {l s='Is Shopylinker suitable for start-up stores?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse " id="question7">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s='Yes, for newly created stores Shopylinker is the best solution since it provides everything necessary to have an easy-to-manage store from the outset with the set of functionalities necessary to compete on the Internet at the lowest price on the market and without the need to buy additional modules.' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row questionbox ">
                    <a class="question" data-toggle="collapse" href="#question8" role="button"
                       aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question8">
                        {l s='Is it suitable for existing stores?' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                    </a>
                    <div class="collapse" id="question8">
                        <div class="card card-body questbody">
                            <p>
                                {l s='Yes, Shopylinker integrates seamlessly with existing stores, immediately providing them with all the features, modules and tools it includes, resulting in significant time and cost savings. If the store already has modules similar to the functionalities present in Shopylinker, it is possible to deactivate the specific functionalities in the Shopylinker administration. However, we recommend using the features included in Shopylinker, since they are always updated to the latest version of the CMS and avoid compatibility problems.' mod='shopylinkerp'}
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2">
            {include file="module:shopylinkerp/views/templates/admin/sidebar.tpl" var=active}
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
